OL,6,FPolice have warned some vaping liquids
OL,7,Fthat are advertised online as
OL,8,Fcontaining cannabis oil are being
OL,9,Freplaced with spice because it's
OL,10,Fcheaper, ITV News Social Affairs
OL,11,Fcorrespondent Sarah Corker reports
OL,13,FChildren as young as 13 have been
OL,14,Fhospitalised after using vapes spiked
OL,15,Fwith dangerous drugs like spice and
OL,16,Ffentanyl.
OL,18,FITV News analysis of official police
OL,19,Fdata reveals vape spiking is a new
OL,20,Femerging threat.
