OL,3,CGirl 'nearly died' after inhaling vape
OL,4,Cspiked with zombie drug spice
OL,6,FOne teenage girl from Teesside
OL,7,Fcollapsed at school after trying a
OL,8,Freusable vape containing the zombie
OL,9,Fdrug spice while she was in a
OL,10,Fclassroom.
OL,12,F"It was scary," she said. "The teacher
OL,13,Fwas talking to me but I was throwing
OL,14,Fup and passing out."
OL,16,F'Polly', 13, whose identity we are
OL,17,Fprotecting due to her young age, told
OL,18,FITV News she had been left traumatised
OL,19,Fby the "near death" experience in
OL,20,FDecember.
