OL,6,F"When I was in the ambulance, the lady
OL,7,Fsaid to me, 'Don't close your eyes in
OL,8,Fcase you don't wake back up'. I kept
OL,9,Flooking at her, but everything kept
OL,10,Fgoing weird."
OL,12,FSpice is a synthetic substance known
OL,13,Fas the zombie drug because in extreme
OL,14,Fcases it can cause breathing
OL,15,Fdifficulties, psychosis and muscle
OL,16,Fspasms. The class B drug is also
OL,17,Fhighly addictive.
