OL,6,FThe teenager was rushed to hospital
OL,7,Fwhere doctors later told her mother
OL,8,FDeborah that if her daughter had taken
OL,9,F"one more puff" she could have had a
OL,10,Fheart attack.
OL,12,F"They said 'If she'd have had a little
OL,13,Fmore, she could have had a cardiac
OL,14,Farrest', which made me even more
OL,15,Fscared," she told ITV News. "It was
OL,16,Fvery frightening. I thought I was
OL,17,Fgoing to lose her."
