OL,6,F"It's incredibly dangerous for young
OL,7,Fpeople to be using vapes, and these
OL,8,Fillegal vapes pose a real risk not
OL,9,Fonly to the children using them, but
OL,10,Feveryone who comes in contact with
OL,11,Fthem," said Grainne Hallahan from
OL,12,FTeacher Tapp.
OL,14,FHeadteacher Glyn Potts told ITV News
OL,15,Fthe issue is "incredibly concerning"
OL,17,FAcross England, headteachers have
