OL,6,FAt Newman RC College near Oldham, a
OL,7,Fchild collapsed at the school gates
OL,8,Fafter inhaling a vape spiked with an
OL,9,Funknown drug.
OL,11,FHeadteacher Glyn Potts told ITV News:
OL,12,F"I'm incredibly concerned because we
OL,13,Fjust don't know what these young
OL,14,Fpeople are ingesting, but we do know
OL,15,Fthere are criminal gangs who are
OL,16,Fputting things in the vapes that are
OL,17,Fcausing real damage.
