OL,6,FThe Manchester Drug Analysis and
OL,7,FKnowledge Exchange, known as the
OL,8,FMANDRAKE Lab, was created at
OL,9,FManchester Metropolitan University in
OL,10,F2016 to help police forces tackle an
OL,11,F"epidemic of psychoactive substances"
OL,12,Fin the city.
