OL,6,FProfessor Rachel Isba, a consultant in
OL,7,Fpaediatric public health medicine,
OL,8,Fsaid her team work closely with each
OL,9,Fyoung person to explore their level of
OL,10,Fnicotine dependency, but she also
OL,11,Fwarned that it was often impossible to
OL,12,Fknow what children were inhaling.
OL,14,F"There is just such a wide variety of
OL,15,Fvapes available, some have other
OL,16,Fsubstances in deliberately, some have
OL,17,Fother substances in accidentally," she
OL,18,Fsaid.
